{"tid":1901962,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"(抗疫同痕)召喚所有想踩roller既屯門天水圍人(2020年版)","createTime":"2020-02-28T05:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T00:14:26.000Z","uid":89287,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e8951814d802590683d250d0efb75a4d8ea63d74","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人有興趣踩ROLLER/一直都有踩 只不過以前屯門區搵唔到人踩而迫不得已去其他地方搵人踩呢?<br />\n<br />\n可能以前係咁 但係而家你絕不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以前都係成日一個人玩 因為完全搵唔到志同道合既人<br />\n但係當我每日無間斷都落去玩既時候 開始識到一班踩ROLLER既人<br />\n所以如果你係住屯門附近 而因為返工/學業或者其他因素覺得出去周圍踩好麻煩既話 歡迎你加入我地<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既係我地既FACEBOOK PAGE PM留低你既電話+點叫你 我會加你入我地既GROUP<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tmrollerskating?ref=hl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftmrollerskating%3Fref%3Dhl&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=7e36803b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tmrollerskating?ref=hl</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你有朋友係住屯門又或者屯門附近<br />\n而又自己玩緊/覺得周圍去好煩<br />\n希望你可以比呢個POST佢睇 考慮黎唔黎JOIN我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為見到最近有D流浪ROLLER友 如果想既話歡迎黎一齊玩<br />\n不過想自己一兩個FD玩都冇所謂 如果想JOIN就直接踩入黎啦<br />\n想學野我地會教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要你肯學 我地肯教<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想PM WTS咁MK既話<br />\n可以每逢星期五晚9點之後黎屯門公園ROLLER埸搵我地<br />\n又或者係街見到有人踩緊ROLLER叫停佢吹水問野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">會踩既時間:<br />\n星期五晚9-11屯門公園<br />\n星期日晚7-10天水圍</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3d6a0cf44c6378040bf22c76a739987b6f494bc4","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"Q: ROLLER係咪有好多種唔同玩法?<br />\n<br />\nA: 無錯 ROLLER除左就咁勁踩之外仲有好多玩法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FEnOPFQlD9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFEnOPFQlD9A&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=14f301c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FEnOPFQlD9A</a> 呢種係Aggressive<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NKFROW45Io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2NKFROW45Io&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=10495dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NKFROW45Io</a> 呢種係花式過樁(Slalom)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7qDqh-wvElc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7qDqh-wvElc&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=c9c47048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7qDqh-wvElc</a> 呢種係花式剎車 (Slide)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cojSRhxA2-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcojSRhxA2-4&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=90934cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cojSRhxA2-4</a> 踩街都可以踩得好型<br />\n<br />\nQ: 如果我想學花式既話應該去邊到?<br />\n<br />\nA: 基本上上面既片簡單既花式我地都可以教到你(例如簡單既平花同剎車 踩街既跳轉180度/360度)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 玩ROLLER危唔危險架?<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔危險 只要你戴足護具( 護手 護膝 護肘) 如果你仲係驚死既可以戴埋頭盔同籃球果種防跌褲 咁樣你想傷都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 如果有時我想自己玩既話應該如何入手?<br />\n<br />\nA: 呢段鬼佬片有齊哂咁多基本野<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8Gs_eyIPFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL8Gs_eyIPFA&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=9e9e7fbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8Gs_eyIPFA</a> 如果你黎問既話我地可以親自示範比你睇同直接教你"},{"pid":"4ca1384a694229aa9ab899a88bafadd5fc9dd72c","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"舊post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1121538/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1121538/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5bc804945f8ddee64ae97e43188fc206e059a0a8","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"另外有小小自家拍既花式片 再高級既我地已經冇人玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSavannth Heel Heel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3xZbooa1KGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3xZbooa1KGM&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=8a615792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3xZbooa1KGM</a><br />\n<br />\nFakie Unity Heel Toe:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I25cBvxqrP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DI25cBvxqrP4&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=f0f374f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I25cBvxqrP4</a><br />\n<br />\nBack Slide:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8TTVgobKYQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8TTVgobKYQk&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=1f118fe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8TTVgobKYQk</a><br />\n<br />\nCross Parallel Toe Toe:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b9cTI9_2umY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db9cTI9_2umY&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=88c13d87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b9cTI9_2umY</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣快D PM我地一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tmrollerskating?ref=hl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftmrollerskating%3Fref%3Dhl&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=7e36803b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tmrollerskating?ref=hl</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"e7c5ab00c85234f46588353eea03952d664fab4b","tid":1901962,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"好型咁 下次帶枝消毒酒精一齊落嚟玩玩"},{"pid":"48396d1bc9c21d101488e100ba65003044b9f648","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7c5ab00c85234f46588353eea03952d664fab4b","tid":1901962,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"好型咁 下次帶枝消毒酒精一齊落嚟玩玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a95f9b9fd7b74ff168a6c6c5e87dd5e08f02362","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eaa646f344a470bc89bc2ca4bbbaad5971cfc18","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7abb3b8b8f4a30e0cd330e63a22a2d5541b69c","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0307ef3e34ebe997598a8c588ba170e5a172fa7a","tid":1901962,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"